    public class ChildrenMatcher
extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.impl.BaseMatcher<ChildrenMatch>
    Generated pattern matcher API of the org.eclipse.viatra.addon.viewers.runtime.model.patterns.children pattern, providing pattern-specific query methods.

    Use the pattern matcher on a given model via on(ViatraQueryEngine), e.g. in conjunction with ViatraQueryEngine#on(Notifier).

    Matches of the pattern will be represented as ChildrenMatch.

    Original source: 

     @QueryExplorer(checked = false)
 pattern children(parent:Item, child:Item) {
        Containment.source(c, parent);
        Containment.target(c, child);
 }

    ChildrenMatch, ChildrenProcessor, ChildrenQuerySpecification
